verbose_text: Comparative co-cultures of basal and luminal breast cancer cell lines with fibroblasts showed differential expression of numerous interleukines and chemokines (including IL-6, IL-8, CXCL1, CXCL3, and TGFbeta) by basal cell lines and increased migration in vitro in basal tumors.
evidence: expression of numerous interleukines and chemokines
